com.nimbusds.openid.connect.messages
Class UserInfoResponse

java.lang.Object
  com.nimbusds.openid.connect.messages.UserInfoResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Message, Response, SuccessResponse
public class UserInfoResponse
extends java.lang.Object
implements SuccessResponse

UserInfo response.

The UserInfo claims may be passed as a plain JSON object or as a plain, signed or encrypted JSON Web Token (JWT). Use the appropriate constructor for that.

Example JSON object representing a UserInfo response: 

 {
   "user_id"     : "248289761001",
   "name"        : "Jane Doe",
   "given_name"  : "Jane",
   "family_name" : "Doe",
   "email"       : "janedoe@example.com",
   "picture"     : "http://example.com/janedoe/me.jpg"
 }

Version:
0.9 (2012-05-17)
Author:
